        {
            "id": 5890465,
            "title": "中國全國政協十四屆三次會議閉幕",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據中國《央視》報導，今天（10 日）上午 9 時，全國政協十四屆三次會議在北京人民大會堂舉行閉幕會。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>閉幕會通過了：</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>政協第十四屆全國委員會第三次會議關於常務委員會工作報告的決議；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>政協第十四屆全國委員會第三次會議關於政協十四屆二次會議以來提案工作情況報告的決議；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>政協第十四屆全國委員會提案委員會關於政協十四屆三次會議提案審查情況的報告；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>政協第十四屆全國委員會第三次會議政治決議。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中國人民政治協商會議第十四屆全國委員會第三次會議在完成各項議程後閉幕。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5890465",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 14:00:09",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 5890733,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電千金股退群 傳產股冒出頭 跌116點收22459點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電今 (10) 日再度跌破千元關卡，拖累大盤跌逾百點，且其他電子權值股並無太多表現，終場跌 116.92 點或 0.52%，以 22459.15 點作收，5 日線得而復失，成交量 3379.9 億元。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股今天大多走跌，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 跌破千元大關，收 998 元，跌幅 0.7%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 以 172 元收平盤，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 跌幅沈重，跌逾 4%。另外，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 小漲 0.13%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 跌 0.92%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>生技族群今天表現弱勢，康霈 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6919-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板，北極星藥業 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6550:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6550\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6550-TW</a>)、保瑞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6472:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6472\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6472-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%，青松健康 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6931:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6931\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6931-TW</a>)、懷特 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4108:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4108\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4108-TW</a>)、泰福 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6541:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6541\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6541-TW</a>) 也都跌逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>以各類指數觀察，今天傳產族群大多上漲。玻璃族群表現亮眼，台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>) 大漲逾半根停板，凱撒衛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1817:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1817\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1817-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，和成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1810-TW</a>)、中釉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1809:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1809\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1809-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%。另外，台塑四寶今天也有表現，台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 及台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 皆漲逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>食品類股也成盤面亮點，大飲 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1213-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，聯華食 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1231-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，統一 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1216:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1216\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1216-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，福懋油 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1225:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1225\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1225-TW</a>)、味王 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1203:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1203\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1203-TW</a>)、卜蜂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1215:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1215\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1215-TW</a>)、愛之味 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1217:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1217\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1217-TW</a>)、泰山 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1218:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1218\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1218-TW</a>) 皆漲逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
